      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "White Knight, Armored Warrior",
        "Client": "Jealous Husband",
        "Description": "My beloved honey-bunny\u0027s all,\r\n\u0022Barioth\u0027s so awe-inspiring,\r\nMagnamalo\u0027s got an air of\r\ndanger. Both are so cool!\u0022\r\nWhat\u0027s so cool about them!? You\r\ntake the scoundrels swaying my\r\nsweetie\u0027s heart down a peg!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Barioth and a Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Chevalier blanc et guerrier",
        "Client": "Mari jaloux",
        "Description": "Ma ch\u00E9rie a un gros faible pour\r\nle Barioth et le Magnamalo,\r\nelle les trouve charismatiques\r\net super cool. Franchement,\r\nje comprends pas. Tu pourrais\r\nleur r\u00E9gler leur compte ?\r\n\u00C7a lui ouvrirait les yeux...",
